  "texts": [
    "In accordance with the objectives of this study, which aimed to define the guiding principles of DeSci, a synthesis of the answers provided by the experts was conducted.",
    "The synthesis resulted in the definition of five categories, summarizing a total of 27 themes.",
    "Table 14 presents an overview of the synthesis that was conducted to define the guiding principles of DeSci.",
    "Because some of the answers provided by the experts included multiple themes, the overall percentage exceeded 100%.",
    "Themes such as 'Integrity' and 'Validation', which were both cited by four of the experts, were summarized in one category that was cited by 19 of the 39 experts (48.7%)."
